Let's Help Moe!! Moe has A.L.S. and he can no longer talk or hold his daughter. He speaks using his eyes on a computer... or by moving one eyebrow for a Yes or No question. ...But, what Moe does have that most people don't, is Punk rock! 
Punk Rock is a community. Let's, as a community, help out one of our own. 
I'm auctioning off my "MoeFX" 22" kick drum head. All of the money from this auction will go directly to Moe and his family. I will personally match what the head sells for.

Thank you very much!! -Smelly

LINK FOR AUCTION IN BIO * 
If you don’t want to bid on the head, but want to help go to “go fund me website and search for “punk rockers unite”.
#NoMoeALS #nofx #moefx

Released 27 years ago today on @epitaphrecords. Favorite track? 
Here’s what Fatty had to say about the album some years ago:
‘I don't remember that much about this album. Two days after we finished, Erik checked himself into a rehab and stayed there for two months and he has been totally sober ever since. Cool. He won't even eat chicken if it has wine sauce on it. Anyway, I don't remember how long this album took, but I do remember it took me a fuck of a long time to sing. Standard.’ #nofx #27club #epitaphrecords
